This software was developed for the VeeShare: Decentralised P2P EV Charging
Network & Grid Flexibility Audit simulation and reproducibility evidence
package, carried out under the PowerBoost Open Call / GreenGrid Eurocluster
innovation audit.

Funding acknowledgement:
This activity has received support from the GreenGrid Eurocluster project
under the European Union Single Market Programme (SMP-COSME).

Scope:
This repository contains simulation, benchmark, reproducibility, synthetic-data,
chart-generation, and audit-evidence code only. It does not contain production
platform code, commercial deployment logic, real user data, payment
infrastructure, DSO integrations, OCPP production integrations, token or
crypto logic, or operational charger-control software.

All numerical outputs are simulation-derived and require independent pilot
validation before operational, regulatory, or investment use.